Alice wants to send a message to Bob in secure way. <br>
Alice encrypted a plaintext P<sub>A</sub> = ¡°IMISSYOU¡± = 0x494D495353594F55 by using DES and obtained ciphertext C<sub>A</sub> = 0xFA26ED1833264435. <br>
Alice sent the ciphertext C<sub>A</sub> and the secret key to Bob. 
The secret key was encrypted by converting each of its letters to a pair of digits giving its position in the typewriter keyboard. 
More precisely, the following table is used.
